data.text: A vote in 2020 for any Republican candidate for the Senate is a vote to return #MoscowMitch (aka #NRAMitch) as the Senate majority leader. We need to remind voters in Maine, Colorado, South Carolina, Iowa, Arizona, New Hampshire, etc. of that every single day.
